transcript:
Customer: 요오
Agent: Assalam o Alaikum, mein Ahmed bol raha hoon UBL se. Aap ki madad kese kar sakta hoon?
Customer: رحمت مجھے بیلنس انکوائری کرنی ہے
Agent: Zaroor, barah-e-karam apna TPIN batayen, chaar alag digits mein.
Agent: Shukriya. Ab barah-e-karam verification ke liye apna account number batayen.
Customer: 11223344
Agent: Aap ke account ka balance 0 hai.
Agent: Agar aap ka koi aur sawal ho to batayen.
Customer: نہیں ہے زیرو بھائی
Agent: Agar aap chahte hain ke main dubara check karoon, to barah-e-karam apna account number phir se batayen.
Customer: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8
Agent: Aap ke account ka balance 0 hai. Agar aap ka koi aur sawal ho to batayen.
Customer: Paglu!
Agent: Maazrat chahta hoon, lagta hai kuch masla ho raha hai. Barah-e-karam aik dafa phir apna account number theek se batayen.
